      "text": [
        "400 - وَقَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ اَلْبَاقِرُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَسُّ اَلْمَيِّتِ عِنْدَ مَوْتِهِ وَ بَعْدَ غُسْلِهِ وَ اَلْقُبْلَةُ لَيْسَ بِهَا بَأْسٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.400 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"Touching a deceased person at the time of their death and after their washing, and kissing them, is not an issue”."
        ]
      }
    },
